      • getProgress

        public int getProgress()
        Provides the wizard's current state of progress as percentage. The default logic is to calculate the progress based on number of screens completed relative to total number of wizard screens available. This may be overriden to provide instance specific custom logic.
        Returns:
        Returns an integer value between 0-100 on success else -1 for error
